    <note>Zhou(1) Wan [505] Li(2) Nangong's [1066] son-in-law (twice: sororate). His son Yuanqing's [3251] father-in-law was Lou(2) Shou's [1265] son Tang [3620]. Yuanqing's son-in-law was Lou(2) Tang's grandson, Yi(b). Zhejiang TZ, 124.18a; XNYL, 155.8a, 178.2a; Liu Caishao, WJ, 5.15b; Lou Yue, WJ, 101.13a, 105.12b. CBD, 2, 1456-7.</note>
